description:
This is a 31 minute workout called '30 Min FULL BODY CALISTHENICS WORKOUT at Home | Follow Along' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Follow along with this full body Calisthenics workout you can do at home without equipment. This is a bodyweight workout designed to improve your strength and mobility. I've included beginner and more advanced exercise variations making this suitable for mixed ability levels.
